case-organizer (1.1.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Policy-compliant install to /usr/lib.
  * Harden postinst to ignore empty FS root.
  * Ship systemd unit + tmpfiles; no systemctl in scripts.
  * Add copyright.
  * Use adduser to create service user 'caseorg'.
  * Added options to add case-laws to case file.
  * Added option to read and manage case notes.

